---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { CTASection } from '../components/sections/CTASection';
---

<Layout 
  title="Energy Resources & Guides | Open Energy Services" 
  description="Read our comprehensive guides on home energy efficiency, solar panels, heat pumps, insulation, and government funding in the UK."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-bg-grey min-h-[60vh]">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Energy efficiency guides and insights.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-12 font-medium">
        We're currently building our resource library. Check back soon for comprehensive guides on insulation, solar panels, heat pumps, and navigating government funding schemes.
      </p>

      <div class="p-12 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-4">Guides coming soon</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">
          In the meantime, if you have any questions about energy efficiency improvements or funding eligibility, please don't hesitate to reach out to our team directly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <CTASection client:visible />
</Layout>